 {'action': 'created', 'author': 'lmammino', 'comment_id': 329536138.0, 'datetime': '2017-09-14 16:26:32+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_0', 'text': 'I did a number of changes and I think this is now ready to be merged.

Latest version is never shown in versions lists, but it can be used as an alias in the urls.

Also when accessing the latest version (as `/docs/latest`) every dropdown now displays the correct latest release tag as selected.

@allevo, @username_1, please double check if this looks like the expected behaviour to you before I proceed with the merge.', 'title': None, 'type': 'comment'}]

